      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAYDEN'S FANCY (1) finished a 3 length third last start over 520m at this track in a slick 29.93. Hard to top on the time from last start. ZIPPING CRUELLA (3) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from four tries. Recorded a 2.5 lengths win (29.72) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. WHERE'S IVY (2) jumped from this box last time and also the same course and distance to score a Grade 5 win (29.92). Has good speed and aided by a low draw. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. EUREKA MAC (5) has a solid strike rate at this distance.",
